\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {S3}{\ignorespaces Left: TSNE embedding of model's `at-a-glance' (before searching for solution) organization of tasks (neural net activations), after first wake/sleep cycle. Middle: at-a-glance organization after last wake/sleep cycle. Right: TSNE visualization of programs actually used to solve tasks; intuitively, how model organizes tasks after searching for a solution. We convert each program into a feature vector by counting the \# times each library routine is used, and then embed those feature vectors.\relax }}{5}}
